title: Freestyle MX Rider Lands in middle of Bull Ring
description: A rider at the norco fair hits the ramp and his bike bogs out right at the lip and has no where to go but into the middle of the bull ring pit. He shattered both of his ankles as well. Everyone hope for him to have a speedy recovery!
